propertyAttribute.label: hadGeneration
propertyAttribute.comment: The _optional_ Generation involved in an Entity's Derivation.

propertyAttribute.label: qualifiedStart
propertyAttribute.comment: If this Activity prov:wasStartedBy Entity :e1, then it can qualify how it was started using prov:qualifiedStart [ a prov:Start;  prov:entity :e1; :foo :bar ].

propertyAttribute.label: atLocation
propertyAttribute.comment: The Location of any resource.

propertyAttribute.label: describesService
propertyAttribute.comment: relates a generic provenance query service resource (type prov:ServiceDescription) to a specific query service description (e.g. a prov:DirectQueryService or a sd:Service).

propertyAttribute.label: has_anchor
propertyAttribute.comment: Indicates anchor URI for a potentially dynamic resource instance.

propertyAttribute.label: used
propertyAttribute.comment: A prov:Entity that was used by this prov:Activity. For example, :baking prov:used :spoon, :egg, :oven .

propertyAttribute.label: wasAttributedTo
propertyAttribute.comment: Attribution is the ascribing of an entity to an agent.

propertyAttribute.label: actedOnBehalfOf
propertyAttribute.comment: An object property to express the accountability of an agent towards another agent. The subordinate agent acted on behalf of the responsible agent in an actual activity.

propertyAttribute.label: wasInformedBy
propertyAttribute.comment: An activity a2 is dependent on or informed by another activity a1, by way of some unspecified entity that is generated by a1 and used by a2.

propertyAttribute.label: provenance pingback
propertyAttribute.comment: Relates a resource to a provenance pingback service that may receive additional provenance links about the resource.

propertyAttribute.label: wasEndedBy
propertyAttribute.comment: End is when an activity is deemed to have ended. An end may refer to an entity, known as trigger, that terminated the activity.

propertyAttribute.label: qualifiedInfluence
propertyAttribute.comment: Because prov:qualifiedInfluence is a broad relation, the more specific relations (qualifiedCommunication, qualifiedDelegation, qualifiedEnd, etc.) should be used when applicable.

propertyAttribute.label: qualifiedEnd
propertyAttribute.comment: If this Activity prov:wasEndedBy Entity :e1, then it can qualify how it was ended using prov:qualifiedEnd [ a prov:End;  prov:entity :e1; :foo :bar ].

propertyAttribute.label: qualifiedGeneration
propertyAttribute.comment: If this Activity prov:generated Entity :e, then it can qualify how it performed the Generation using prov:qualifiedGeneration [ a prov:Generation;  prov:entity :e; :foo :bar ].

propertyAttribute.label: qualifiedUsage
propertyAttribute.comment: If this Activity prov:used Entity :e, then it can qualify how it used it using prov:qualifiedUsage [ a prov:Usage; prov:entity :e; :foo :bar ].

propertyAttribute.label: wasRevisionOf
propertyAttribute.comment: A revision is a derivation that revises an entity into a revised version.

propertyAttribute.label: hadRole
propertyAttribute.comment: The _optional_ Role that an Entity assumed in the context of an Activity. For example, :baking prov:used :spoon; prov:qualified [ a prov:Usage; prov:entity :spoon; prov:hadRole roles:mixing_implement ].

propertyAttribute.label: has_provenance
propertyAttribute.comment: Indicates a provenance-URI for a resource; the resource identified by this property presents a provenance record about its subject or anchor resource.

propertyAttribute.label: hadUsage
propertyAttribute.comment: The _optional_ Usage involved in an Entity's Derivation.

propertyAttribute.label: hadPlan
propertyAttribute.comment: The _optional_ Plan adopted by an Agent in Association with some Activity. Plan specifications are out of the scope of this specification.

propertyAttribute.label: qualifiedPrimarySource
propertyAttribute.comment: If this Entity prov:hadPrimarySource Entity :e, then it can qualify how using prov:qualifiedPrimarySource [ a prov:PrimarySource; prov:entity :e; :foo :bar ].

propertyAttribute.label: qualifiedCommunication
propertyAttribute.comment: If this Activity prov:wasInformedBy Activity :a, then it can qualify how it was influenced using prov:qualifiedCommunication [ a prov:Communication;  prov:activity :a; :foo :bar ].

propertyAttribute.label: wasInfluencedBy
propertyAttribute.comment: Because prov:wasInfluencedBy is a broad relation, its more specific subproperties (e.g. prov:wasInformedBy, prov:actedOnBehalfOf, prov:wasEndedBy, etc.) should be used when applicable.

propertyAttribute.label: wasDerivedFrom
propertyAttribute.comment: The more specific subproperties of prov:wasDerivedFrom (i.e., prov:wasQuotedFrom, prov:wasRevisionOf, prov:hadPrimarySource) should be used when applicable.

propertyAttribute.label: qualifiedInvalidation
propertyAttribute.comment: If this Entity prov:wasInvalidatedBy Activity :a, then it can qualify how it was invalidated using prov:qualifiedInvalidation [ a prov:Invalidation;  prov:activity :a; :foo :bar ].

propertyAttribute.label: hasProvenanceService
propertyAttribute.comment: Indicates a provenance query service that can access provenance related to its subject or anchor resource.

propertyAttribute.label: qualifiedQuotation
propertyAttribute.comment: If this Entity prov:wasQuotedFrom Entity :e, then it can qualify how using prov:qualifiedQuotation [ a prov:Quotation;  prov:entity :e; :foo :bar ].

propertyAttribute.label: qualifiedRevision
propertyAttribute.comment: If this Entity prov:wasRevisionOf Entity :e, then it can qualify how it was revised using prov:qualifiedRevision [ a prov:Revision;  prov:entity :e; :foo :bar ].

propertyAttribute.label: mentionOf
propertyAttribute.comment:
prov:mentionOf is used to specialize an entity as described in another bundle. It is to be used in conjuction with prov:asInBundle.

prov:asInBundle is used to cite the Bundle in which the generalization was mentioned.

propertyAttribute.label: qualifiedAttribution
propertyAttribute.comment: If this Entity prov:wasAttributedTo Agent :ag, then it can qualify how it was influenced using prov:qualifiedAttribution [ a prov:Attribution;  prov:agent :ag; :foo :bar ].

propertyAttribute.label: qualifiedDerivation
propertyAttribute.comment: If this Entity prov:wasDerivedFrom Entity :e, then it can qualify how it was derived using prov:qualifiedDerivation [ a prov:Derivation;  prov:entity :e; :foo :bar ].

propertyAttribute.label: wasAssociatedWith
propertyAttribute.comment: An prov:Agent that had some (unspecified) responsibility for the occurrence of this prov:Activity.

propertyAttribute.label: influencer
propertyAttribute.comment: Subproperties of prov:influencer are used to cite the object of an unqualified PROV-O triple whose predicate is a subproperty of prov:wasInfluencedBy (e.g. prov:used, prov:wasGeneratedBy). prov:influencer is used much like rdf:object is used.

propertyAttribute.label: hadActivity
propertyAttribute.comment: The _optional_ Activity of an Influence, which used, generated, invalidated, or was the responsibility of some Entity. This property is _not_ used by ActivityInfluence (use prov:activity instead).

propertyAttribute.label: qualifiedDelegation
propertyAttribute.comment: If this Agent prov:actedOnBehalfOf Agent :ag, then it can qualify how with prov:qualifiedResponsibility [ a prov:Responsibility;  prov:agent :ag; :foo :bar ].

propertyAttribute.label: asInBundle
propertyAttribute.comment:
prov:asInBundle is used to specify which bundle the general entity of a prov:mentionOf property is described.

When :x prov:mentionOf :y and :y is described in Bundle :b, the triple :x prov:asInBundle :b is also asserted to cite the Bundle in which :y was described.

propertyAttribute.label: wasQuotedFrom
propertyAttribute.comment: An entity is derived from an original entity by copying, or 'quoting', some or all of it.

propertyAttribute.label: qualifiedAssociation
propertyAttribute.comment: If this Activity prov:wasAssociatedWith Agent :ag, then it can qualify the Association using prov:qualifiedAssociation [ a prov:Association;  prov:agent :ag; :foo :bar ].

propertyAttribute.label: wasStartedBy
propertyAttribute.comment: Start is when an activity is deemed to have started. A start may refer to an entity, known as trigger, that initiated the activity.

propertyAttribute.label: endedAtTime
propertyAttribute.comment: The time at which an activity ended. See also prov:startedAtTime.

propertyAttribute.label: atTime
propertyAttribute.comment: The time at which an InstantaneousEvent occurred, in the form of xsd:dateTime.

propertyAttribute.label: generatedAtTime
propertyAttribute.comment: The time at which an entity was completely created and is available for use.

propertyAttribute.label: invalidatedAtTime
propertyAttribute.comment: The time at which an entity was invalidated (i.e., no longer usable).

propertyAttribute.label: startedAtTime
propertyAttribute.comment: The time at which an activity started. See also prov:endedAtTime.

propertyAttribute.label: provenanceUriTemplate
propertyAttribute.comment: Relates a provenance service to a URI template string for constructing provenance-URIs.

classAttribute.label: EntityInfluence
classAttribute.comment: EntityInfluence provides additional descriptions of an Entity's binary influence upon any other kind of resource. Instances of EntityInfluence use the prov:entity property to cite the influencing Entity.

classAttribute.label: Revision
classAttribute.comment: An instance of prov:Revision provides additional descriptions about the binary prov:wasRevisionOf relation from some newer prov:Entity to an earlier prov:Entity. For example, :draft_2 prov:wasRevisionOf :draft_1; prov:qualifiedRevision [ a prov:Revision; prov:entity :draft_1; :foo :bar ].

classAttribute.label: Start
classAttribute.comment: An instance of prov:Start provides additional descriptions about the binary prov:wasStartedBy relation from some started prov:Activity to an prov:Entity that started it. For example, :foot_race prov:wasStartedBy :bang; prov:qualifiedStart [ a prov:Start; prov:entity :bang; :foo :bar; prov:atTime '2012-03-09T08:05:08-05:00'^^xsd:dateTime ] .

classAttribute.label: InstantaneousEvent
classAttribute.comment: An instantaneous event, or event for short, happens in the world and marks a change in the world, in its activities and in its entities. The term 'event' is commonly used in process algebra with a similar meaning. Events represent communications or interactions; they are assumed to be atomic and instantaneous.

classAttribute.label: Association
classAttribute.comment: An instance of prov:Association provides additional descriptions about the binary prov:wasAssociatedWith relation from an prov:Activity to some prov:Agent that had some responsiblity for it. For example, :baking prov:wasAssociatedWith :baker; prov:qualifiedAssociation [ a prov:Association; prov:agent :baker; :foo :bar ].

classAttribute.label: Influence
classAttribute.comment: Because prov:Influence is a broad relation, its most specific subclasses (e.g. prov:Communication, prov:Delegation, prov:End, prov:Revision, etc.) should be used when applicable.

classAttribute.label: Dictionary
classAttribute.comment: A given dictionary forms a given structure for its members. A different structure (obtained either by insertion or removal of members) constitutes a different dictionary.

classAttribute.label: ServiceDescription
classAttribute.comment: Type for a generic provenance query service. Mainly for use in RDF provenance query service descriptions, to facilitate discovery in linked data environments.

classAttribute.label: Generation
classAttribute.comment: An instance of prov:Generation provides additional descriptions about the binary prov:wasGeneratedBy relation from a generated prov:Entity to the prov:Activity that generated it. For example, :cake prov:wasGeneratedBy :baking; prov:qualifiedGeneration [ a prov:Generation; prov:activity :baking; :foo :bar ].

classAttribute.label: Bundle
classAttribute.comment: Note that there are kinds of bundles (e.g. handwritten letters, audio recordings, etc.) that are not expressed in PROV-O, but can be still be described by PROV-O.

classAttribute.label: Plan
classAttribute.comment: There exist no prescriptive requirement on the nature of plans, their representation, the actions or steps they consist of, or their intended goals. Since plans may evolve over time, it may become necessary to track their provenance, so plans themselves are entities. Representing the plan explicitly in the provenance can be useful for various tasks: for example, to validate the execution as represented in the provenance record, to manage expectation failures, or to provide explanations.

classAttribute.label: AgentInfluence
classAttribute.comment: It is not recommended that the type AgentInfluence be asserted without also asserting one of its more specific subclasses.

classAttribute.label: End
classAttribute.comment: An instance of prov:End provides additional descriptions about the binary prov:wasEndedBy relation from some ended prov:Activity to an prov:Entity that ended it. For example, :ball_game prov:wasEndedBy :buzzer; prov:qualifiedEnd [ a prov:End; prov:entity :buzzer; :foo :bar; prov:atTime '2012-03-09T08:05:08-05:00'^^xsd:dateTime ].

classAttribute.label: ActivityInfluence
classAttribute.comment: It is not recommended that the type ActivityInfluence be asserted without also asserting one of its more specific subclasses.

classAttribute.label: Delegation
classAttribute.comment: An instance of prov:Delegation provides additional descriptions about the binary prov:actedOnBehalfOf relation from a performing prov:Agent to some prov:Agent for whom it was performed. For example, :mixing prov:wasAssociatedWith :toddler . :toddler prov:actedOnBehalfOf :mother; prov:qualifiedDelegation [ a prov:Delegation; prov:entity :mother; :foo :bar ].

classAttribute.label: Quotation
classAttribute.comment: An instance of prov:Quotation provides additional descriptions about the binary prov:wasQuotedFrom relation from some taken prov:Entity from an earlier, larger prov:Entity. For example, :here_is_looking_at_you_kid prov:wasQuotedFrom :casablanca_script; prov:qualifiedQuotation [ a prov:Quotation; prov:entity :casablanca_script; :foo :bar ].

classAttribute.label: Derivation
classAttribute.comment: The more specific forms of prov:Derivation (i.e., prov:Revision, prov:Quotation, prov:PrimarySource) should be asserted if they apply.

classAttribute.label: Usage
classAttribute.comment: An instance of prov:Usage provides additional descriptions about the binary prov:used relation from some prov:Activity to an prov:Entity that it used. For example, :keynote prov:used :podium; prov:qualifiedUsage [ a prov:Usage; prov:entity :podium; :foo :bar ].

classAttribute.label: PrimarySource
classAttribute.comment: An instance of prov:PrimarySource provides additional descriptions about the binary prov:hadPrimarySource relation from some secondary prov:Entity to an earlier, primary prov:Entity. For example, :blog prov:hadPrimarySource :newsArticle; prov:qualifiedPrimarySource [ a prov:PrimarySource; prov:entity :newsArticle; :foo :bar ] .

classAttribute.label: Invalidation
classAttribute.comment: An instance of prov:Invalidation provides additional descriptions about the binary prov:wasInvalidatedBy relation from an invalidated prov:Entity to the prov:Activity that invalidated it. For example, :uncracked_egg prov:wasInvalidatedBy :baking; prov:qualifiedInvalidation [ a prov:Invalidation; prov:activity :baking; :foo :bar ].

classAttribute.label: Communication
classAttribute.comment: An instance of prov:Communication provides additional descriptions about the binary prov:wasInformedBy relation from an informed prov:Activity to the prov:Activity that informed it. For example, :you_jumping_off_bridge prov:wasInformedBy :everyone_else_jumping_off_bridge; prov:qualifiedCommunication [ a prov:Communication; prov:activity :everyone_else_jumping_off_bridge; :foo :bar ].

classAttribute.label: Attribution
classAttribute.comment: An instance of prov:Attribution provides additional descriptions about the binary prov:wasAttributedTo relation from an prov:Entity to some prov:Agent that had some responsible for it. For example, :cake prov:wasAttributedTo :baker; prov:qualifiedAttribution [ a prov:Attribution; prov:entity :baker; :foo :bar ].

classAttribute.label: ProvenanceService
classAttribute.comment: Type for a generic provenance query service. Mainly for use in RDF provenance query service descriptions, to facilitate discovery in linked data environments.
